reviewText: It was very poor quality and out of date.  It had very little history of policing.  I trashed it.  I wanted to show it in a class on policing it did not make the grade.

This is very outdated! I do not recommend it for training purposes. It does not cover the history and current changes. I used it for a College class and was  very dissapointed. Need to find a new video on history to date.
